Title: Age of Empires II: Definitive Edition — Hotfix 37906
Age of Empires II: Definitive Edition — Update 37650
Changes: {'General': ['The Supplies technology is no longer available to the Chinese, Cumans, Huns, Khmer, Lithuanians, Mayans, Mongols, and Tatars.', 'Watch Towers can no longer be built in the Dark Age if one is automatically generated at the start of the match (e.g. on the Fortress map).', 'Hussar: Reduced the length of the attack animation from 1.89 to 1.35 seconds (equivalent to Light Cavalry). Title: Age of Empires II: Definitive Edition — Update 36906
Changes:
{'General': ['The civilization bonuses which provide additional villagers to the Chinese and Mayans and a bonus llama to the Incas have been disabled in the Empire Wars game mode.', 'Fishermen can now drop food they’ve collected at Docks.
